[Hopefully, internationally reputable diagnostic and/or research
centres will express their willingness to receive representative
samples from China and offer their services for comparative studies
with PRRS virus strains from other sources including Viet Nam,
pertaining to infectivity, pathogenicity, serology, and genetic
profiling, and to check the possible involvement/interaction with
other pathogens. ProMED-mail will gladly publish such offers. - Mod.AS]
